name: Square One (Mr.Nobody3675)
description:
PLAY AT YOUR OWN RISK!

This is a rage game, and you might press your keyboard so hard that it becomes so deep, you couldn't even use it anymore.

I challenged myself: MADE FOR THE THEME: LOOKS CAN BE DECIEVING

I interpreted this into, the platformer playing tricks on you. With platforms not working (Intentional Bug). 

LIMITATION: ONLY ONE TYPE 

(Quadlirateral, in this case.)
